metadata.name: Free Dimmel Bottle #2
metadata.description: Dimmel is a multi-channel brand with communication channels in the form of physical and informational products. The first channel is the dimmel.ru website where we have been building communication for more than seven years with customers as well as in social networks. The second channel is the physical product of the brand - bottled water that will be launched in the third quarter of 2022. The third channel is NFT backed by produced water. By holding 'Free dimmel bottle' in your wallet, you become part of the third channel.
